              "name": "lmT",
              "fill": "$light-text-primary",
              "content": "3.1 线性代数基础",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 24,
              "fontWeight": "600",
              "letterSpacing": -0.5
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "HgwPO",
              "name": "lmB1",
              "fill": "$light-text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "线性代数是数学的一个分支，它在机器学习和深度学习中占据着核心地位。理解线性代数的基本概念对于深入理解深度学习算法至关重要。\n\n标量（scalar）是一个单独的数，与线性代数中研究的其他大部分对象不同，它通常用小写的斜体字母来表示。向量（vector）是一列有序排列的数。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "BRo6O",
              "name": "lmB2",
              "fill": "$light-text-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "矩阵（matrix）是一个二维数组，其中的每一个元素被两个索引所确定。我们通常会赋予矩阵粗体的大写变量名称，比如 A。",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 15,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
